          "key": "answer_requirements",
          "value": {
            "speakerName": "Professor Clark",
            "text": "The goal is a completed Stewardship Field Journal. Catch fish to log them in your catalog. Then debone them to complete your entries. You must also earn 2,000 gold to pay your tuition fees.",
