        {
          "key": "graduation_review_part1",
          "value": {
            "speakerName": "Professor Clark",
            "text": "One season ago, I stood here and spoke of balance and choices. Today, we see the results of your journey. Your Stewardship Field Journal tells a story of skill and responsibility.",
